25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：在学习凭据提取、票据攻击和域后渗透的安全研究者。\n阅读前提：了解 LSASS、NTLM、Kerberos 与域环境基础概念。\n核心收获：掌握 Mimikatz 常用模块与典型域攻击链条。\n说明：实操前请确认实验环境与授权边界，版本差异会影响命令输出。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"后渗透（Post-Exploitation）阶段是渗透测试中价值最高的环节。在获取初始访问和提升权限之后，攻击者需要提取凭据、建立持久化、深入域环境。Mimikatz 是 Windows 后渗透中最具代表性的工具，它能从内存中提取明文密码、NTLM Hash 和 Kerberos 票据。本文将全面讲解 Mimikatz 的核心功能，以及黄金票据、白银票据、DCSync 等高级域攻击技术。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"mimikatz-简介与功能模块","children":["Mimikatz 简介与功能模块",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#mimikatz-简介与功能模块","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Mimikatz 由法国安全研究员 Benjamin Delpy 开发，是 Windows 安全研究领域最重要的工具之一。它通过直接访问 Windows 安全子系统（LSASS 进程）来提取认证凭据。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"核心模块概览","children":["核心模块概览",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#核心模块概览","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",["$","table",null,{"children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"children":"模块"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"功能"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"典型用途"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"sekurlsa"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"LSASS 进程凭据提取"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"提取密码、Hash、票据"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"lsadump"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"LSA 数据库操作"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"SAM 数据库导出、DCSync"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"kerberos"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Kerberos 操作"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"票据导出/导入/伪造"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"crypto"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"加密操作"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"证书导出"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"vault"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Windows 凭据保管库"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"提取保存的凭据"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"dpapi"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"数据保护 API"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"解密 Chrome 密码等"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"token"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"令牌操作"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"令牌提升和模拟"}]]}]]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"基本使用","children":["基本使用",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#基本使用","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2d","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"凭据提取","children":["凭据提取",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#凭据提取","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"sekurlsalogonpasswords","children":["sekurlsa::logonpasswords",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#sekurlsalogonpasswords","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"这是 Mimikatz 最常用的命令，从 LSASS 进程内存中提取所有已登录用户的凭据。"}],"\n","$L2e","\n",["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"注意"}],"：Windows 10 / Server 2016 之后，默认禁用了 WDigest 明文密码缓存。可以通过修改注册表重新启用："]}],"\n"]}],"\n","$L2f","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"sekurlsa-其他命令","children":["sekurlsa 其他命令",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#sekurlsa-其他命令","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L30","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"创建-lsass-转储","children":["创建 LSASS 转储",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#创建-lsass-转储","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L31","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"lsadumpsam","children":["lsadump::sam",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#lsadumpsam","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"从 SAM 数据库中提取本地用户的 NTLM Hash。"}],"\n","$L32","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"ntlm-hash-提取与利用","children":["NTLM Hash 提取与利用",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#ntlm-hash-提取与利用","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L33","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"黄金票据golden-ticket攻击","children":["黄金票据（Golden Ticket）攻击",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#黄金票据golden-ticket攻击","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":["黄金票据是 Kerberos 攻击的终极手段。通过获取 ",["$","code",null,{"children":"krbtgt"}]," 账户的 NTLM Hash，攻击者可以伪造任意用户的 TGT（票据授权票据），从而以任意身份访问域内任何资源。"]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"获取-krbtgt-hash","children":["获取 krbtgt Hash",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#获取-krbtgt-hash","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L34","\n","$L35","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"伪造黄金票据","children":["伪造黄金票据",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#伪造黄金票据","children":"$L36"}]]}],"\n","$L37","\n","$L38","\n","$L39","\n","$L3a","\n","$L3b","\n","$L3c","\n","$L3d","\n","$L3e","\n","$L3f","\n","$L40","\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","$L41","\n","$L42","\n","$L43","\n","$L44","\n","$L45","\n","$L46","\n","$L47","\n","$L48","\n","$L49","\n","$L4a","\n","$L4b","\n","$L4c","\n","$L4d","\n","$L4e","\n","$L4f","\n","$L50","\n","$L51","\n","$L52","\n","$L53","\n","$L54","\n","$L55","\n","$L56","\n","$L57","\n","$L58","\n","$L59","\n","$L5a","\n","$L5b","\n","$L5c","\n","$L5d","\n","$L5e","\n","$L5f","\n","$L60","\n","$L61","\n","$L62","\n","$L63"]
